UPDATE dbo.Disease SET overview = 'Megaloblastic anemiais ananemia(ofmacrocyticclassification) that results from inhibition ofDNA synthesisduringred blood cellproduction.When DNA synthesis is impaired, thecell cyclecannot progress from the G2 growth stage to the mitosis (M) stage. This leads to continuing cell growth without division, which presents as macrocytosis.
