UPDATE dbo.Disease SET overview = 'Progressive rubella panencephalitis (PRP)is aneurological disorderwhich may occur in a child with congenitalrubella.It is a slow viral infection of the brain characterized by chronicencephalitis, usually manifesting between 819 years of age.
