UPDATE dbo.Disease SET overview = 'True hermaphroditism, sometimes referred to asovotesticular disorder,is anintersexcondition in which an individual is born withovarianandtesticulartissue. Commonly one or bothgonadsis anovotestiscontaining both types of tissue.Ovotesticular disorders are a family of disorders which includes true hermaphroditism.Although similar in some ways tomixed gonadal dysgenesis, the conditions can be distinguished histologically.' WHERE code = 'Q7847568';
UPDATE dbo.Disease SET overview = 'Tuberculoid leprosyis a form ofleprosycharacterized by solitaryskin lesionsthat are asymmetrically distributed with few lesions and well demarcated edges. There is also early and marked nerve damage. It tends to heal spontaneously.:345Tuberculoid leprosy is characterized by the formation ofepithelioid cellgranulomaswith a large number ofepithelioid cells. In this  form of leprosy Mycobacterium leprae are either absent from the lesion or occur in very small numbers. This type of leprosy is the most benign and the least contagious.' WHERE code = 'Q7850839';
