UPDATE dbo.Disease SET overview = 'Urologic diseasesor conditions includeurinary tract infections,kidney stones,bladder controlproblems, andprostateproblems, among others. Some urologic conditions do not affect a person for that long and some are lifetime conditions.Kidney diseases are normally investigated and treated bynephrologists, while the specialty ofurologydeals with problems in the other organs.Gynecologistsmay deal with problems ofincontinencein women.Diseases of other bodily systems also have a direct effect on urogenital function. For instance, it has been shown thatproteinreleased by the kidneys indiabetes mellitussensitizes the kidney to the damaging effects ofhypertension.Diabetesalso can have a direct effect onurinationdue toperipheral neuropathies, which occur in some individuals with poorly controlled diabetics.' WHERE code = 'Q7900883';
